    "description": "If you're a passionate Floor Manager with drive and ambition, Nippon Paint Store Holdings Services in Allahabad is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Nippon Paint Store Holdings Services:\nNippon Paint Store Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in KPI Management\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Loss Prevention\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Flexible working hours\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Allahabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Nippon Paint Store Holdings Services!",
